import { Button, ButtonGroup, Flex, Spacer, Text, useColorMode } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import React from "react";


 const Header=()=>{
    const { colorMode, toggleColorMode } = useColorMode()
 
    return(
    <Flex my={4}>
        <Text>My TMDB</Text>
        <Spacer/>
        <ButtonGroup  gap={8}>
        <Button>Movies</Button>
        <Button>TV</Button>
        </ButtonGroup>
        <Spacer/>
       
        <Spacer/>
        <ButtonGroup gap={2}>
        <Button>Log In</Button>
        <Button>Register</Button>
        <Button onClick={toggleColorMode}>
        Toggle {colorMode === 'light' ? 'Dark' : 'Light'}
        </Button>
        </ButtonGroup>
    </Flex>)
    
}


export default Header
